{"tid":1165151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣6月9日遊行反對草案直上大會","createTime":"2019-05-21T15:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T12:07:48.000Z","uid":230382,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"36c56ce2489b2176a8a5d8568de5a9457ce4924e","tid":1165151,"uid":230382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:03:10.000Z","msg":"民陣將於6月9日舉行反《逃犯條例》修訂草案遊行。民陣召集人岑子杰表示，如果政府硬推修例，行動會更激烈，包括包圍立法會。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超昨日表示，《逃犯條例》修訂草案將於6月12日直接提交大會並恢復二讀辯論。民陣表示，6月9日會舉行遊行以作回應，召集人岑子杰表示，目標是30萬人參與，當日下午3時集合，會由銅鑼灣東角道出發，遊行至金鐘添美道立法會外，要求政府撤回修例。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰又表示，如果政府硬推修例，民陣逼於無奈會會發起更激烈行動，包括包圍立法會，亦會組織全港設立超過200個街站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1005133-香港-【逃犯條例】民陣6月9日舉行遊行+若政府硬推會包圍立會\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1005133-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A36%E6%9C%889%E6%97%A5%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%2B%E8%8B%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A1%AC%E6%8E%A8%E6%9C%83%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=8ae5918d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1005133-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A36%E6%9C%889%E6%97%A5%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%2B%E8%8B%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A1%AC%E6%8E%A8%E6%9C%83%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83&h=59ba30f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1005133-香港-【逃犯條例】民陣6月9日舉行遊行+若政府硬推會包圍立會</a>"},{"pid":"a43a4d0b7c6f481f029cca9a389f96872f890455","tid":1165151,"uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"一定去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對送中條例"},{"pid":"9835890786ddb58e254a21aac7d29a2d29fa8993","tid":1165151,"uid":5627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT